title: Bird (disambiguation)
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Bird (disambiguation)

Bird may refer to:

NPCs[edit | edit source]

  • Eagles:
    • Desert eagle
    • Giant eagle
    • Jungle eagle
    • Polar eagle
  • Hunter creatures:
    • Copper longtail
    • Cerulean twitch
    • Crimson swift
    • Golden warbler
    • Tropical wagtail
  • 'Birds-Eye' Jack
  • Chompy
    • Not to be confused with: Chompy chick, the pet from chompy bird hunting;
  • Cormorant
  • Crow
  • Desert Phoenix
    • Not to be confused with: Phoenix, the Wintertodt pet;
  • Drake
  • Duck (Common)
  • Duck (Kourend Woodland)
  • Ducklings
  • Gull
  • Gyr falcon, used in falconry;
  • Owl
  • Parrot, ordering players around in Trouble Brewing;
  • Pelican
  • Pigeon
  • Puffin
  • Seagull
  • Swan

Monsters[edit | edit source]

  • Creature Creation:
    • Jubster
    • Newtroost
    • Swordchick
  • Other monsters:
    • Aviansie
    • Baby Roc, fought during the My Arm's Big Adventure quest;
    • Bird
    • Cockatrice
    • Chicken
    • Chompy bird
    • Desert phoenix
    • Duck
    • Duckling
    • Entrana firebird, fought during the Heroes' Quest;
    • Evil Chicken
    • Giant Roc, fought during the My Arm's Big Adventure quest;
    • Jubbly bird
    • Kree'arra
    • Mounted terrorbird gnome
    • Oomlie bird
    • Pheasant, encountered in the Freaky Forester random event;
    • Penguin
    • Rooster
    • Terrorbird
    • Vulture
    • Undead chicken

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Bird meat:
    • Raw bird meat
    • Skewered bird meat
    • Roast bird meat
    • Burnt bird meat
  • Hunter items:
    • Bird snare
    • Bird snare pack
  • Woodcutting items:
    • Bird nest
    • Bird's egg
  • Bird book, used in the Eagles' Peak quest.
  • Bird feed, used in the Biohazard quest.
  • Book on chickens
  • Chicken outfit
  • Chompy bird hat
  • Evil chicken outfit
  • Evil chicken's egg
  • Feathers
  • Pigeon cage, used in the Biohazard and One Small Favour quests.
  • Terrorbird wing, and its polished version, used in the Rag and Bone Man II quest.

Other[edit | edit source]

  • Big Chompy Bird Hunting, a quest.
  • Chompy chick, a pet
  • Eagles' Peak, a quest.
  • Evil Chicken's Lair, a location.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
